THE DOG HOUSE HAS AN INDOOR AND SMALL OUTDOOR PLAY AREA. IT IS LOCATED AT 310 PROVIDENCE HWY WESTWOOD MA 02090

For more information please visit http://www.thedoghousewestwood.com/

Dogs must be current with the following vaccinations before entering the facility. Distemper/Parvo, Rabies, and Bordatella. All dogs must be on a flea and tick preventative.Â  Upon admission all dogs must be free from any condition that could potentially jeopardize the health and safety of other dogs.
